metadata.name: Metalik Buterin
metadata.description:
Title: Metalik Buterin 

Description: Unique sculpture, 100% digitally modeled from start to finish by Daiana Lazzarin, inspired by Vitalik Buterin, this 1/1 edition work will be the only one without any other variant, neither colors nor of any kind. It differs from other 3D works by NOT using models downloaded from the Internet with slight modifications as is usually seen in the NFT world. Daiana Lazzarin is a University Art Professor and Professional Sculptress, most of her physical works sold have been sculptures, reliefs and monuments.

Artist: Daiana Lazzarin

Origin: Mendoza, Argentina.

Technique: 3D modeling

Year: 2022
